data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! ASSUMABLE LOAN!! 5.625% INTEREST RATE!! Country living with a city feel! Check out this four bedroom, three bath home located in the amazing City of Gastonia. With over 2300 Square Feet of Heated Living Space, you will be overwhelmed with open space to make your own. You can make two living room areas with a dining area or a living room with a large dining area. Lots of great options! Owners suite comes with a stand up shower and a garden tub with a walk-in closet. This home is sure to please even the most pickiest home buyer. For you privacy lovers, the home comes with a partially fenced yard. Gastonia is a growing and thriving town with a great downtown that is packed with restaurants and shops. Just a little over a 20 minute drive, you will arrive at CLT airport, and a little over 30 mins from all the great pleasures of the City of Charlotte. Home is MINUTES away for the SC Border making the location of this home incredible!!
